    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "cool, thanks. for the guide, can u also write a section that explains why the old experience was so special? like, maybe emphasize the specific ways you handle their preferences or the personal touch you give that a faster, more \"generic\" bot might miss? i want them to feel like they aren't losing anything important.",
